    {
      "level": "H1",
      "text": "Chapter 2 \u2013 Forms of Business Organisation",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Forms of Business Organisation",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "There are different forms of business organizations from which a choice has to be made:",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Sole proprietorship",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Joint Hindu family business",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Partnership",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Joint stock Company",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Cooperative Societies",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Sole Proprietorship",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "It is a form of organisation which is owned, managed and controlled by an individual who",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "bears all the risk and receives all the profit.",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Features",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Formation and closure:",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "It can be established and closed without any legal",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "formalities.",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Liability:",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "The liability of the sole proprietor is unlimited in this form of business",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "organisation.",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Sole risk bearer and profit recipient:",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Being a sole owner, he bears all the risk and",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "receives all the profits.",
      "page": 1
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Control:",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "All the decisions are taken and implemented in the organization by the",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "owner.",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "No separate entity:",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Both owner and business are considered as one in the eyes of",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "law.",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Lack of business continuity:",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Business can be continued till the owner wishes to.",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Merits",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Quick decision making:",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Prompt decision making as all the decisions are to be taken",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "by the owner.",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Confidentiality of information:",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Being a sole owner, it is easy to maintain business",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "secrecy.",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Direct incentive:",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "All the profits are enjoyed by the owner as there is no one to share",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "profits.",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Sense of accomplishment:",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Successful business provides satisfaction to the owner",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "and sense of achievement.",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Ease of formation and closure:",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "No legal formalities for formation and closure of",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "business which makes it easy to start and end the business.",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Limitations",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Limited resources:",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Business can be funded from savings of the owner or money",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "borrowed from friends, relatives.",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Limited life of a business concern:",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Continuity of the business depends on the health",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "and state of mind of the owner.",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Unlimited liability:",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "In case business fails repayment of debts, his personal assets are",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "at risk.",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Limited managerial ability:",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "One person may not possess the ability to manage all",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "the functions.",
      "page": 2
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Joint Hindu Family Business",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "It is a form of business which is owned and managed by members of Hindu undivided family,",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "with the possibility of three successive generations as members in the business.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Features",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Formation:",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Hindu Undivided Family is formed with at least two members of a",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "family having ancestral property. It is governed by Hindu Succession Act, 1956.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Liability:",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "All the members of the family except Karta have limited liability up to",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "their share in the business property.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Control:",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "All the activities in the business organization are controlled by Karta.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Continuity:",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "It can be discontinued if all the members of the family agree to do so.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Minor members:",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Membership in the organization is by birth.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Merits",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Effective control:",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Complete control of business with \u2018Karta\u2019 thus effective decision",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "making.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Continued business existence:",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Business continues till all the members wish to",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "continue and control is transferred to the next elder member in case of death of",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "\u2018Karta\u2019.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Limited liability of members:",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Members of the family enjoy liability limited to their",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "share in the business party.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Increased loyalty and cooperation",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": ": Family members have a sense of belongingness",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "and loyalty, hence, all work with a common objective of growth.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Limitations",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Limited resources:",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Business can be funded mainly from ancestral property, hence",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "limiting the financial resources.",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Unlimited liability of Karta:",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "The personal property of \u2018Karta\u2019 is at risk as he has",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "unlimited liability.",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Dominance of Karta:",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Difference of opinion among members and \u2018Karta\u2019 may cause",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "conflict amongst them.",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Limited managerial skills:",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Karta may not have knowledge and expertise of all the",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "functions performed in the business.",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Partnership",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "According to partnership Act 1932, partnership is the relation between persons who have",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "agreed to share the profits of the business carried on by all or any one of them acting for all.",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Features",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Formation:",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Business is established as per the provisions of partnership Act 1932.",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Liability:",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "All the partners in the business have unlimited liability.",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Risk bearing:",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "All the risk in the business is shared by all the partners.",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Decision making and control:",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "All the decisions are taken in after the consent of all",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "the partners and each partner shares responsibility of running business.",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Continuity:",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Continuity depends upon the partnership deed among the partners at the",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "time of its formation.",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Number of partners:",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Minimum 2 and maximum 50 members [as per the Companies",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "(miscellaneous) Rules 2014}, or maximum could be 100 ( according to Companies",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Act, 2013).",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Mutual agency:",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Each partner is the owner as well as the agent of the firm and agent",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "to other partners.",
      "page": 4
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Merits",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Ease of formation and closure:",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Business can be established and closed with the",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "consent of all the partners as the registration is optional.",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Balanced decision making:",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "All the decisions are taken by consent partners",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "as  partners undertake responsibilities as per their expertise.",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "More funds:",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Funds are provided by all the partners, which increases the scope for",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "large-scale business operation.",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Sharing of risks:",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Business risk and responsibilities are shared among all the partners.",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Secrecy:",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "It is easy to maintain business secrecy as there is no need to submit financial",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "results.",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Limitations",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Unlimited liability:",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Each partner\u2019s liability is extended to their personal property.",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Limited resources:",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Availability of Finance is limited due to the restriction of number",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "of partners.",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Possibility of conflicts:",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "All the partners may have different opinions which create",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "conflict among them.",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Lack of continuity:",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Any conflict between partners or death of a partner may bring",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "business to an end.",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Lack of public confidence:",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "It is difficult for an outsider to ascertain true financial",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "position as there is a lack of availability of financial reports.",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Types of Partners",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Active partner:",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "A partner who contributes capital, shares profits and losses,",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "participates in management and has unlimited liability.",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Sleeping or dormant partner:",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Partner who contributes capital, shares profits and",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "losses and has unlimited liability but does not participate in management.",
      "page": 5
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Secret partner:",
      "page": 6
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "This partner participates in management operations secretly, but does",
      "page": 6
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "contribute in profits and losses.",
      "page": 6
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Nominal partner:",
      "page": 6
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Partner who does not contribute capital and does not share profit",
      "page": 6
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "and losses but allows partnership business to project him or her as partner.",
      "page": 6
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Partner by estoppel:",
      "page": 6
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "An individual who is not a partner but projects himself/herself",
      "page": 6
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "as a partner to an outsider and has unlimited liability.",
      "page": 6
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Partner by holding out:",
      "page": 6
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "An individual who is not a partner but is projected as a",
      "page": 6
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "partner by other partners of the partnership firm and his liability is unlimited.",
      "page": 6
    },
    {
