    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Minor as partner:",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "An individual of age below 18 years can be admitted with mutual consent of all other partners",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "but legally he is not a partner.",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Types of partnership",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Partnership can be categorised on the basis of duration and liability:",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Classification on the basis of duration",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Partnership at will:",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Partnership continues till the partners agree to do so.",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Particular partnership:",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "The partnership formed for a specific task for project or for",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "a specific period of time. It comes to an end after completion of task or expiry of time.",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Classification on the basis of liability",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "General partnership:",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Partnership where all partners have joint and unlimited",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "liability",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Limited partnership:",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Partnership where all partners have limited liability and at least",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "one partner must have unlimited liability.",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Partnership deed",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "A written document where all the terms and conditions of partnership are mentioned. It",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "generally has following clauses:",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Name of firm",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Nature of firm",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Duration of partnership",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Duties and obligations of partners",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Valuation of assets",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Interest on capital and interest on drawings",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Profit-loss sharing ratio",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Salaries and withdrawals of the partners.",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Preparation of accounts and their auditing.",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Procedure for dissolution of firm",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Method of solving disputes.",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Registration",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "It is optional for a partnership firm to get registered with the registrar of firms of the state in",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "which form is situated.",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Consequences of non registration",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "In case of non registration, a partner cannot file a case or file suit against other",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "partners or the partnership firm.",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Firm cannot sue third parties.",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "The form cannot file a case against one or more partners of the firm.",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Procedure for getting firm registered",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Submission of application in prescribed form with the Registrar of Firms.",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Fee deposition with the Registrar.",
      "page": 8
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Receiving certificate of registration after the Registrar is satisfied.",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Cooperative Society",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "An organisation of voluntary people working for a common purpose with an aim to protect",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "economic and social interests of the members. It must be registered under the Cooperative",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Societies Act, 1912.",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Features",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Voluntary membership:",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Any individual irrespective of caste, gender, religion with",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "common interest is free to join or leave a cooperative society as and when he/she",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "desires.",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Legal status:",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Cooperative society has separate identity status distinct from its",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "members, and the registration of such society is also mandatory.",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Limited liability:",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Members have liability limited to their capital contribution.",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Control:",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "All the decision making power is in the hands of an elected managing",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "committee which are chosen by members with one man one vote concept.",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Service motive:",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Society is formed with the motive of providing mutual help to team",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "members.",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Merits",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Equality in voting status:",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Each member has equal right to vote and elect members of",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "the managing committee.",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Limited liability:",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "The liability of members is limited to their capital contribution.",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Stable existence:",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Cooperative societies keep on going irrespective of situations of",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "death, bankruptcy or insanity of its members.",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Economy in operations:",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "The members of the society work voluntarily which helps in",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "reducing costs.",
      "page": 9
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Support from government:",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Government provides support to societies in the form of",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "lower taxes, interest rates and subsidies.",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Ease of formation:",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "No legal formalities are involved in formation of societies.",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Limitations",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Limited resources:",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Capital contribution by the member is the only source of finance,",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "and low dividend also discourages members for the provision of finance to the",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "society.",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Inefficiency in management:",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Members working on voluntary basis may lack",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "necessary expertise and skills, leading to inefficiency in operations and management.",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Lack of secrecy:",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Difficult to maintain secrecy as members disclose all information",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "related to work of the society in the meeting.",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Government control:",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Societies need to follow rules and regulations as stated by the",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "government and submit audited financial reports of the society. However, such",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "government intervention affects the freedom of work for such societies.",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Differences of opinion:",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Difference of opinion as a result of individual interest over",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "the welfare may lead to conflicts amongst members.",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Types of cooperative societies",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Consumer\u2019s cooperative societies:",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Societies formed for providing good quality",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "services and products at a reasonable rate, to protect the interest of consumers.",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Producer\u2019s cooperative societies",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": ": Societies formed for providing good quality and",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "low priced raw materials and other inputs, to protect the interest of producers.",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Marketing cooperative societies:",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Societies for providing services related to",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "marketing of products by small producers.",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Farmer\u2019s cooperative societies:",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Societies formed for providing farmers with better",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "inputs at reasonable rates to improve productivity.",
      "page": 10
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Credit cooperative societies:",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Societies established to provide financial assistance to",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "its members at very reasonable terms.",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Cooperative housing societies:",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Societies formed for constructing houses for its",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "members at reasonable cost.",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Joint Stock Company",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "The Companies Act, 2013 defines, \"A company as an artificial person having a separate legal",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "entity, perpetual succession and a common seal.\"",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Features of a Joint Stock Company",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Artificial person:",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "A company is created by law and has legal status but it does not",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "function like human beings. All business activities are done by the board of directors",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "in the name of the company.",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Separate legal entity:",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "A company has its own identity distinct from its owner with",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "the incorporation of a company.",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Formation:",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Company is formed by fulfilling all the legal formalities as stated under",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Companies Act, 2013.",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Perpetual succession:",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "A company is created by law and can be wound up by law",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "only. Existence of the company is not affected by the status of members.",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Control:",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Business affairs of a company are managed and controlled by the Board of",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Directors.",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Liability:",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "A company has limited liability i.e., liability only to the extent of the",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "capital contribution.",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Common seal:",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "As a company is an artificial legal person, it cannot have a sign on its",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "own/ Hence common seal acts as the official signature for a company. All the official",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "documents must have a common seal for legal binding.",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Risk bearing:",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "The risk of loss is shared by all the shareholders in proportion to their",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "investment in the company.",
      "page": 11
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Merits",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Limited liability:",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Shareholders liability is limited to the investment in the company,",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "thus, there is no risk of losing personal assets.",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Transfer of interest:",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Shares can easily be sold in the market or can be converted into",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "cash.",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Perpetual existence:",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Company's existence is not affected by the status of",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "shareholders, company continues to exist.",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Scope for expansion:",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Companies can raise large amounts of funds from the public as",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "well as borrowings from financial institutions or banks.",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Professional management:",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "large-scale operation requires management by",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "professionals and specialised individuals.",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Limitations",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Complexity in formation:",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Formation of a company requires fulfilling of",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "documentation and legal formalities which makes the procedure lengthy and complex.",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Lack of secrecy:",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "All financial information is disclosed to the general public that there",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "is no confidentiality or secrecy.",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Impersonal work environment:",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Business affairs are managed by professionals not",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "owners, thus, it lacks personal contact with employees and customers.",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Numerous regulations:",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "A company involves various rules and regulations which",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "reduces freedom to work and involves a lot of money, time and effort.",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Delay in decision making:",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Decision making needs to follow a set of hierarchy which",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "may cause delay in taking decisions and actions.",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Oligarchic management:",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Shareholders have very little control over the running of",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "business, thus, the directors take all the decisions which may at times get influenced",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "by their personal interest.",
      "page": 12
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Conflict in interests:",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "It is difficult for management to satisfy everyone as there are",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "too many stakeholders with diverse interests.",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Types of Companies",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Private Company",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "A company must have minimum 2 or maximum 200 members.",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Right to transfer shares is restricted.",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Funds cannot be generated from the general public.",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Uses 'Private Limited' after the company name.",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Public Company",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Minimum 7 members with no limit on maximum members.",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Free to transfer shares.",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Issue shares to the general public.",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Uses 'Public Limited' after the company name.",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Difference between Public and Private Company",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Basis",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Public Company",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Private Company",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Members",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Minimum: 7 members",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Maximum: Unlimited",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Minimum: 2 members",
      "page": 13
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
