      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Choice of Form of Business Organisation",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Cost and ease in setting up the organisation:",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "It is easy to start sole proprietorship",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "with minimum cost and legal requirements whereas formation of a company is a",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "complex task with lengthy legal procedure. But partnership has the advantage of less",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "legal requirements with low cost.",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Liability:",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "In sole proprietorship and partnership, the liability of owner or partners is",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "unlimited but in cooperative societies and companies, members have limited liability.",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Continuity:",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "In sole proprietorship and partnership, continuity is affected by death and",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "insolvency of the owners but cooperative societies, companies and Hindu undivided",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "family enjoy perpetual existence.",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Management ability:",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "In sole proprietorship, it is difficult that the owner may have",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "expertise in all functions but in other forms of business, division of work is possible",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "which leads to better decision making.",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Capital consideration:",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "In case of large scale of operation, company form is more",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "suitable but in case of small scale of operation, partnership or sole proprietorship can",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "be chosen.",
      "page": 14
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Degree of control:",
      "page": 15
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "If the owner wants all the control in his hand the sole",
      "page": 15
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "proprietorship may be preferred but if the owner is ready to share control, then he can",
      "page": 15
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "adopt partnership or company form.",
      "page": 15
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Nature of business:",
      "page": 15
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "For trading and services, sole proprietorship and partnership",
      "page": 15
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "form can be chosen. For manufacturing, a company form of organisation can be",
